00:15:32.500 --> 00:15:34.510
But that's a really neat idea.

00:15:34.510 --> 00:15:38.630
The determinant of the
transformation matrix is

00:15:38.630 --> 00:15:43.020
essentially a scaling
factor on the area

00:15:43.020 --> 00:15:44.420
